title: BRIEF-High Liner Foods Q4 Adjusted Earnings Per Share C$0.19
text: February 21, 2018 / 1:55 PM / a minute ago BRIEF-High Liner Foods Q4 Adjusted Earnings Per Share C$0.19 Reuters Staff Feb 21 (Reuters) - High Liner Foods Inc: * HIGH LINER FOODS REPORTS OPERATING RESULTS FOR THE FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR OF 2017 * Q4 ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE C$0.19 * QTRLY ‍SALES INCREASED BY $54.2 MILLION TO $263.0 MILLION COMPARED TO $208.8 MILLION IN Q4 2016​ * QTRLY EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.43‍​ * Q4, FY 2017‍ NET INCOME REFLECTS NON-CASH INCOME TAX RECOVERY OF $11.2 MILLION DUE TO TCJA Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
